<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">جره يجره جرا:</span> جذبه<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">يجره:</span> <span style="color:#008000">(وَأَلْقَى الأَلْوَاحَ وَأَخَذَ بِرَأْسِ أَخِيهِ يَجُرُّهُ إِلَيْهِ)</span> <span style="color:#950000">"١٥٠/ الأعراف "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
